{
 "translations": [
  {
   "offset": 8,
   "len": 65,
   "en": "a scarred man with a gap-toothed grin and large, calloused hands.",
   "zh": "滿臉刀疤的男子，齜牙而笑，兩手滿是老繭。",
   "note": "DESC"
  },
  {
   "offset": 83,
   "len": 39,
   "en": "\"Don't like talking when I'm fighting!\"",
   "zh": "「打架的時候不喜歡說話！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 144,
   "len": 15,
   "en": "\"Hello, hello.\"",
   "zh": "「你好，你好。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 172,
   "len": 56,
   "en": "\"Right. You been here before.\" He studies you carefully.",
   "zh": "「對了，你來過。」他仔細打量著你。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 231,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"What'll it be?\"",
   "zh": "「要什麼？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 254,
   "len": 46,
   "en": "\"Hey, what's it look like, I'm a mind reader?\"",
   "zh": "「哎，你以為我能讀心術嗎？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 303,
   "len": 29,
   "en": "\"Do ya want @arms or @armor?\"",
   "zh": "「你要@arms（武器）還是@armor（甲冑）？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 350,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"Come by my shop when I'm open!\"",
   "zh": "「開店的時候再來！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 531,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"And my mutter said I was thick.\"",
   "zh": "「我娘還說我笨呢。」",
   "note": "mutter=母親(德語借詞俚語)"
  },
  {
   "offset": 567,
   "len": 57,
   "en": "\"You can @buy's arms from me or @sell me yer used stuff.\"",
   "zh": "「你可以向我@buy（買）器，或者把舊裝備@sell（賣）我。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 635,
   "len": 60,
   "en": "\"@Enrik. Enrik the @Hammer's what I'm known as 'round here.\"",
   "zh": "「@Enrik（恩里）克。這附近都叫我@Hammer（鐵鎚）恩里克。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 706,
   "len": 20,
   "en": "\"I prefers @Hammer.\"",
   "zh": "「我喜歡人叫我@Hammer（鐵鎚）。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 737,
   "len": 48,
   "en": "\"They call me that 'cause I's got a good @left.\"",
   "zh": "「因為我的@left（左拳）很厲害，所以才這樣叫。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 801,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"Keep it up and I'll show ya,\" he growls.",
   "zh": "「繼續這樣，讓你見識見識，」他低吼道。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 852,
   "len": 31,
   "en": "\"Yeah, gotta get back ta work.\"",
   "zh": "「嗯，得回去幹活了。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 888,
   "len": 27,
   "en": "He gives you a blank stare.",
   "zh": "他茫然地盯著你。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1059,
   "len": 43,
   "en": "\"Sorry, none of you's got anything I need.\"",
   "zh": "「抱歉，你們沒有我要的東西。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1136,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "\"Aye, $Y has somethin' interestin'...\"",
   "zh": "「嗯，$Y有件有趣的東西……」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1236,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
   "zh": "「你們哪位？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1473,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "\"Which item?\" ",
   "zh": "「哪件東西？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1565,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"Will you take #7 gold for that $0, $Y?\" ",
   "zh": "「$Y，這件$0你願意賣#7枚金幣嗎？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1619,
   "len": 24,
   "en": "\"Mebbe some other time.\"",
   "zh": "「也許改天吧。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1651,
   "len": 23,
   "en": "\"Mebbe somethin' else?\"",
   "zh": "「要別的嗎？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1690,
   "len": 52,
   "en": "\"Done!\" $N hands $Y #7 gold pieces and takes the $0.",
   "zh": "「成交！」$N遞給$Y #7枚金幣，取走了$0。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1798,
   "len": 24,
   "en": "\"Changed your mind, eh?\"",
   "zh": "「改主意了，是吧？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2158,
   "len": 24,
   "en": "\"That $1 costs #1 gold.\"",
   "zh": "「$1要#1枚金幣。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2185,
   "len": 18,
   "en": "\"Interested, $Y?\" ",
   "zh": "「有意嗎，$Y？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2246,
   "len": 39,
   "en": "\"But that'd make you o'erburdened, $Y!\"",
   "zh": "「但那樣你就超重了，$Y！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2335,
   "len": 7,
   "en": "\"Good!\"",
   "zh": "「好！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2344,
   "len": 48,
   "en": "After accepting $Y's gold, $N hands over the $1.",
   "zh": "$N收下$Y的金幣，將$1交了過去。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2401,
   "len": 36,
   "en": "\"But you don't got enough gold, $Y!\"",
   "zh": "「但你的金幣不夠，$Y！」",
   "note": ""
  }
 ],
